methods.stream:
Create a DoubleStream over the remaining elements of this DoubleColumnIterator. The result must be
 closed in order to ensure resources are released. A
 try-with-resources block is strongly encouraged.

:return: (java.util.stream.DoubleStream) A DoubleStream over the remaining contents of this iterator. Must be closed.

text: ColumnIterator implementation for chunk sources of primitive doubles.
